### Install git ###
# sudo apt-get install git
###

### Installation on Ubuntu/yaVDR ###
#
# git clone git://github.com/seahawk1986/vdr-skin-pearlhd_remix.git
# cd vdr-skin-pearhd_remix
# sudo cp -R pearlhd_NG /var/lib/vdr/plugins/text2skin/
# sudo cp themes/* /var/lib/vdr/themes/
#
###

To use the skin restart your VDR.




